videos.headline: Colorado State WR snags TD for 1st score
videos.description: QB K.J. Carta-Samuels hits WR Preston Williams on a 5-yard touchdown as Colorado State takes an early 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Colorado State QB fools camera man on fake play
videos.description: C.J. Carta-Samuels fools the entire stadium on a keep-option play to put Colorado State up 14-0.
